The iStore has revealed local pricing for Apple’s new iPad Air and iPad Mini. The two new models feature a 10.5-inch display and 7.9-inch display, respectively, and offer Wi-Fi or Wi-Fi+Cellular connectivity. Colour options are silver, space grey, or gold. The iStore has also listed Apple’s new AirPods, along with local pricing. The new AirPods include hands-free Siri access, 50% longer talk time, and optional wireless charging. Local pricing for the new iPads is listed below. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-299714" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-iPad-Mini.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="589" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-iPad-Mini.jpg 816w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-iPad-Mini-435x400.jpg 435w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-iPad-Mini-768x707.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/New-iPad-Mini-467x430.jpg 467w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Local pricing for the new AirPods is listed below. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-300122" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Apple-Airpods-2.png" alt="Apple Airpods 2" width="640" height="431" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Apple-Airpods-2.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Apple-Airpods-2-300x202.png 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Apple-Airpods-2-594x400.png 594w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Apple-Airpods-2-639x430.png 639w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />